  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK708">
<l>mukanōkki niṟka vamaiyu makanōkki</l>
<l>yuṟṟa tuṇarvārp peṟiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the king gets those who by looking into his mind can understand (and remove) what has occurred (to him) it is enough that he stand looking at their face.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
